The first map got some positive feedback from the server i play on. They didnt like the color scheme said it was too plan. 

I added some color the the map.
Some props.
Ladders.
Made the map a little more difficult.

Although the map looks bigger it's actually the same. There are invisible walls that separate the players from the extended environment. I added the environment as a cosmetic thing.

U can probably try the map at 74.52.37.5:27016 (Evil Smurft Gun Game Knife Pro server)

Thanks for all the support and GG
